OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775815515
OL,3,CGiving children tablets instead of
OL,4,Cliquid medicine could cut NHS costs `
OL,5,Cexperts
OL,7,FGiving children with a certain medical
OL,8,Fcondition tablets instead of liquid
OL,9,Fmedicine could save the NHS tens of
OL,10,Fthousands of pounds per patient each
OL,11,Fyear, experts have said.
OL,13,FResearchers found patients as young as
OL,14,Fseven were successfully able to switch
OL,15,Fto pills, and often preferred them to
OL,16,Fthe taste of liquid medicine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
