CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775815515
OL,3,CGiving children tablets instead of
OL,4,Cliquid medicine could cut NHS costs `
OL,5,Cexperts
OL,7,FExperts from Great Ormond Street
OL,8,FHospital (Gosh) are now planning to
OL,9,Fassess whether patients as young as
OL,10,Ffour can successfully switch to
OL,11,Fcheaper tablets.
OL,13,FAcademics at the world-renowned
OL,14,Fchildren's hospital wanted to examine
OL,15,Fthe switch among patients with a
OL,16,Fcondition called congenital
OL,17,Fhyperinsulinism (CHI).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775815515
OL,3,CGiving children tablets instead of
OL,4,Cliquid medicine could cut NHS costs `
OL,5,Cexperts
OL,7,FChildren with the condition, which
OL,8,Fleads to high levels of insulin in the
OL,9,Fbody, are given a treatment called
OL,10,Fdiazoxide to keep their blood sugar
OL,11,F(glucose) levels stable.
OL,13,FThey must take treatment multiple
OL,14,Ftimes a day depending on their insulin
OL,15,Fand glucose levels.
OL,17,FUntil now children were given the
OL,18,Ftreatment as a liquid, with liquid
OL,19,Fdiazoxide coming with a price tag of
OL,20,F#15.50 per 50mg.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775815515
OL,3,CGiving children tablets instead of
OL,4,Cliquid medicine could cut NHS costs `
OL,5,Cexperts
OL,7,FTablet diazoxide costs just #1.15 per
OL,8,F50mg.
OL,10,FExperts have estimated that switching
OL,11,Ffrom liquid to tablets could save the
OL,12,FNHS #40,000 per patient per year.
OL,14,FThe condition affects one in every
OL,15,F30,000-40,000 children.
OL,17,FGosh experts conducted a project on 19
OL,18,Fpatients aged seven to 13 to see
OL,19,Fwhether the switch was viable.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775815515
OL,3,CGiving children tablets instead of
OL,4,Cliquid medicine could cut NHS costs `
OL,5,Cexperts
OL,7,FPatients were monitored to ensure
OL,8,Ftheir blood glucose levels remained
OL,9,Fstable and asked about how the change
OL,10,Fin medication format had impacted them.
OL,12,FJess Manktelow, who has CHI and has
OL,13,Fbeen a Gosh patient since she was 15
OL,14,Fmonths old, was one of the children
OL,15,Fwho took part in the project.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775815515
OL,3,CGiving children tablets instead of
OL,4,Cliquid medicine could cut NHS costs `
OL,5,Cexperts
OL,7,FHer school and family life was
OL,8,Forganised around taking liquid
OL,9,Fdiazoxide multiple times a day, which
OL,10,Fneeds to be stored at room temperature
OL,11,Fin a glass bottle and drawn up with a
OL,12,Fsyringe.
OL,14,F"I would always get a lot of questions
OL,15,Fabout the medication when I would go
OL,16,Faway camping or at airport for
OL,17,Fholidays," she said.
OL,19,F"It would always be hard to explain
OL,20,Fwhy I need it so much, but it isn't
OL,21,Falways an easy condition to explain."
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@JO]{D@AOU}D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775815515
OL,3,CGiving children tablets instead of
OL,4,Cliquid medicine could cut NHS costs `
OL,5,Cexperts
OL,7,FThe 11-year-old, from Kent, was
OL,8,Fswitched to diazoxide tablets in April
OL,9,F2025.
OL,11,F"It has made a big difference taking
OL,12,Fmedicine that doesn't taste horrible,"
OL,13,Fshe added.
OL,15,F"There were times where I didn't want
OL,16,Fto take it because of the taste.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@fO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775815515
OL,3,CGiving children tablets instead of
OL,4,Cliquid medicine could cut NHS costs `
OL,5,Cexperts
OL,7,F"It makes things very easy for me now,
OL,8,FI'm able to do it myself and it
OL,9,Fdoesn't take up as much time at school
OL,10,For when I'm doing things I like, like
OL,11,Fclimbing, it doesn't have as much
OL,12,Fimpact and that makes me happy."
OL,14,FHer mother Steph Manktelow added: "We
OL,15,Fwere so excited when the team told us
OL,16,Fwe could switch to the diazoxide
OL,17,Ftablets.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@`O]vD@cOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775815515
OL,3,CGiving children tablets instead of
OL,4,Cliquid medicine could cut NHS costs `
OL,5,Cexperts
OL,7,F"We'd been hoping for some time, we
OL,8,Fknew it was a better solution and
OL,9,Fwould allow Jess to have control over
OL,10,Fher condition and that is very
OL,11,Fimportant."
OL,13,FKate Morgan, Gosh clinical nurse
OL,14,Fspecialist who co-led the project,
OL,15,Fsaid: "We knew the potential this
OL,16,Ftrial had for savings, but the scale
OL,17,Fof the quality-of-life improvements
OL,18,Ffor children and their families we are
OL,19,Fseeing is something we didn't
OL,20,Fanticipate.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@KO]wD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775815515
OL,3,CGiving children tablets instead of
OL,4,Cliquid medicine could cut NHS costs `
OL,5,Cexperts
OL,7,F"Children are so much more than their
OL,8,Fdiagnoses ` they have full lives and
OL,9,Ffamilies and their illnesses affects
OL,10,Feveryone, so it is very important we
OL,11,Fdo all we can to make simple, positive
OL,12,Fchanges that impact everyone for the
OL,13,Fbetter."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775815515
OL,3,CGiving children tablets instead of
OL,4,Cliquid medicine could cut NHS costs `
OL,5,Cexperts
OL,7,FProject co-lead Dr Antonia Dastamani,
OL,8,Fconsultant of paediatric endocrinology
OL,9,Fand diabetes at Gosh, added: "It is
OL,10,Fcommon practice to ask patients how
OL,11,Fthey're finding treatment, or how they
OL,12,Ffeel when they have injections, but we
OL,13,Fnever thought to ask patients about
OL,14,Fthe taste of medicines and whether
OL,15,Fthey like them.
OL,26,@qD@^OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
